data.description: Perfect 4 bedroom 2.5 bath Colonial in a beautiful location. Open and sunny floor plan.  Hardwood floors. All full sized bedrooms and a must see primary bedroom. 2 car garage. perfect kitchen for entertaining with tons of cabinet space. Bonus rooms in finished basement. Over 35,000 sq ft lot for privacy. Seller willing to buy down the mortgage rate on this home. PLEASE BOOK SHOWINGS THROUGH SHOWINGTIME
